name: R'EVOL #001 - THE OUTLAW
description:
Welcome to the R'EVOL project. 
A new series of insane characters inspired by the work of KidEight, newly created by upcoming artist Kingsbridge.


MEET #001 - THE OUTLAW

STORY:
"The Outlaw, a one-man army, feared by all who have heard of him. A cherub, passing through the badlands, from the deepest jungle to the farthest mountain, slaying every monster in his path.

Some may call him a hero, his fury, reckless acts of heroism but nobody really seems to know the reason behind why The Outlaw does what he does.

Maybe one day, we will learn of the origin of this trail of blood. But until then, he remains a mysterious hunter, roaming a world of monsters."



Buy his unique PORTRAIT today!
Thank you for supporting young and upcoming artists :)
